data.description:
**All rooms including garage are handicap accessible. **

Due to the a change in the buyers financial situation this house is back on the market.  

This stunning property offers an open concept living area, perfect for entertaining, featuring a stylish kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances.
The master suite is a true retreat, complete with a walk-in closet and a luxurious en-suite bathroom featuring a double vanity, a large shower. The three additional bedrooms are generously sized and offer plenty of closet space. The second bathroom is conveniently located near these bedrooms.
Situated in a peaceful neighborhood, this home benefits from an excellent location in Yukon. You'll be just minutes away from local schools, shopping centers, and dining options. Commuting is a breeze with easy access to Kilpatrick Turnpike.
Don't miss the opportunity to make 9109 NW 81st your new home. Call today to schedule a private showing and experience all this property has to offer.
